rain that actually remembers — across sessions, across agents, across time.\\n\\nA LanceDB-backed OpenClaw memory plugin that stores preferences, decisions, and project context, then auto-recalls them in future sessions.\\n\\nhttps://github.com/openclaw/openclaw\\nhttps://github.com/openclaw/openclaw\\nhttps://www.npmjs.com/package/memory-lancedb-pro\\nhttps://lancedb.com\\n/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/LICENSE\\n\\n ✅ Fully adapted for OpenClaw 2026.3+ new plugin architecture\\n\\n 🔄 Uses before_prompt_build hooks (replacing deprecated before_agent_start)\\n\\n 🩺 Run openclaw doctor --fix after upgrading\\n\\n[English](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README.md) | [简体中文](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_CN.md) | [繁體中文](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_TW.md) | [日本語](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_JA.md) | [한국어](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_KO.md) | [Français](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_FR.md) | [Español](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/master/README_ES.md) | [Deutsch](/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro/blob/mas\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"767cf33243c4bb1c\\\">>>\"\n}"}],"details":{"url":"https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro","finalUrl":"https://github.com/CortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro","status":200,"contentType":"text/html","title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c39e812a124e8dec\">>>\nSource: Web Fetch\n---\nCortexReach/memory-lancedb-pro: Enhanced LanceDB memory plugin for OpenClaw — Hybrid Retrieval (Vector + BM25), Cross-Encoder Rerank, Multi-Scope Isolation, Management CLI · GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c39e812a124e8dec\">>>","extractMode":"markdown","extractor":"readability","externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_fetch","wrapped":true},"truncated":true,"length":2000,"rawLength":1229,"wrappedLength":2000,"fetchedAt":"2026-04-01T06:55:14.746Z","tookMs":1896,"text":"SECURI