{"type":"message","id":"49e81a66","parentId":"2d790f1c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:55:30.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have information about both repos:\n\n1. **lossless-claw-enhanced** by win4r\n   - Fork of Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw\n   - CJK-aware token estimation (fixes CJK text token counting)\n   - Lossless Context Management plugin for OpenClaw\n   - DAG-based summarization system\n\n2. **memory-lancedb-pro** by CortexReach\n   - LanceDB-backed memory plugin for OpenClaw\n   - Hybrid Retrieval (Vector + BM25)\n   - Cross-Encoder Rerank\n   - Multi-Scope Isolation\n   - Management CLI\n   - Fully adapted for OpenClaw 2026.3+ new plugin architecture\n\nThese look legitimate and useful. The user wants me to install them so I don't forget things about them and their context.\n\nLet me check if they can be installed via npm or clawhub. The memory-lancedb-pro mentions it's on npm: https://www.npmjs.com/package/memory-lancedb-pro\n\nLet me check the installation instructions. I'll look for a SKILL.md or installation guide in these repos. Actually, these seem to be OpenClaw plugins. Let me check how to install them.\n\nI should explain to the user what I found and ask if they want me to proceed with installation.","thinkingSignature":"54856a025d47a8f190fcb34fffa153dc8b9a20b479f8bc25ad605d317bd089bb"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，获取到了：\n\n**1. lossless-claw-enhanced** (win4r)\n- 无损上下文管理插件，基于 DAG 摘要系统\n- 修复了 CJK 文本 token 估算不准确的问题（中文/日文/韩文）\n- 替换 OpenClaw 内置的滑动窗口压缩\n\n**2. memory-lancedb-pro** (CortexReach)\n- LanceDB 向量数据库记忆插件\n- 混合检索（Vector + BM25）+ Cross-Encoder 重排\n- 跨 Session/Agent/时间记忆保持和召回\n- 适配 OpenClaw 2026.3+ 新插件架构\n\n---\n\n这两个看起来都是正经的 OpenClaw 插件。要装的话需要通过 npm 安装：\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g lossless-claw-enhanced\nnpm install -g memory-lancedb-pro\n```\n\n你想让我帮你执行安装吗？还是你想自己装？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6985,"output":459,"cacheRead":33363