{"type":"message","id":"8afde10b","parentId":"d250b435","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:21:52.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to authorize commands each time - do they need to go to the backend page each time? They're asking about the authorization flow.\n\nThe user seems to be getting prompted for authorization frequently. They're asking if there's a way to avoid this or if they need to go to a \"backend page\" each time.\n\nThere are a few options:\n1. Set exec.security to \"full\" in the OpenClaw config - this would allow all commands without prompting\n2. Set up an allowlist of specific commands\n3. The current approach where they need to approve each command\n\nLet me explain the options to them clearly.","thinkingSignature":"0db18bb92ca8b215628a31ab6c92df95c197a92848d029128e51f38707c431c1"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 不需要每次都进后台。有几种方式：\n\n**1. 临时方案（现在用的）**\n每次命令会弹授权提示，你直接回复 `/approve xxx allow-once` 就行，不用进后台页面。\n\n**2. 永久方案 - 改配置文件**\n在你的 OpenClaw 配置文件（通常是 `~/.openclaw/config.json` 或 `~/.openclaw/gateway.json`）里加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"exec\": {\n    \"security\": \"full\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n这样所有命令都直接放行，不用每次授权。\n\n你想用哪种？配置文件在 `~/.openclaw/` 目录下，你要我帮你看现在的配置长什么样吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114,"output":274,"cacheRead":20893,"cacheWrite":30341,"totalTokens":51622,"cost":{"input":0.0000342,"output":0.00032879999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0012535799999999998,"cacheWrite":0.011377875,"total":0.012994455}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775028094013,"responseId":"061bfa7e99251c803a88db1269c17137"}}
